
<div class="centered">

  <div id="page" class="arial content">
    <div id="title">
      <h1>Contact</h1>
    </div>
    
    <p>N'hésitez pas à prendre contact par mail, via le formulaire ci-dessous, ou par téléphone au []. Je vous recontacterai au plus tôt.</p>

    <form method="post" class="form-horizontal" action"/contact">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="col-sm-2 control-label">Email</label>
        <div class="col-sm-10">
          <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="Email">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="col-sm-2 control-label">Confirmation email</label>
        <div class="col-sm-10">
          <input type="email" class="form-control" name="confirmEmail" placeholder="Confirmation email">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="col-sm-2 control-label">Objet</label>
        <div class="col-sm-10">
          <input type="text" name="title" class="form-control" placeholder="Objet">
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="inputPassword" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Texte</label>
        <div class="col-sm-10">
          <textarea class="form-control" name="content" placeholder="Votre texte ici" rows="10"></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-2">
          <%= captcha_image_tag %>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-4">
            <%= captcha_answer_tag %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default col-sm-offset-2">Envoyer !</button>

    </form>

  </div>

</div>
